# DevTools dashboard — local environment overrides.
# Copy to `.env.local` (git-ignored) and fill in, then restart the dashboard.

# Operator allowlist for Tailscale exposure (`pnpm tool devtools serve`).
# Comma-separated tailnet LOGINS (the identity you sign in to Tailscale with —
# may differ from your email). When the dashboard is reached over the tailnet,
# Tailscale injects an authoritative Tailscale-User-Login header; the middleware
# 403s any identity not in this list (fail-closed if the list is empty).
# Local 127.0.0.1 access is never gated by this.
DEVTOOLS_ALLOWED_TS_USERS=
